Love Defiled: Verified MCQs
Q.1. Who is the author of the title “Love Defiled”?
(A) Giridhar Jha
(B) Binapani Mohanty
(C) Katherine Mansfield
(D) None of these
Answer: (A) Giridhar Jha
Explanation: “Love Defiled” is written by Giridhar Jha, a well-known journalist and scriptwriter based in Patna.

